The most effective way for new IT-based companies to target both the Islamic and Chinese markets would be to undertake extensive market research and customize their goods and services to fit the particular demands and preferences of each market. Cultural and language variations, as well as local rules and compliance needs, are crucial factors to consider. Additionally, it would be advantageous to form partnerships or collaborations with local firms and organizations in each area in order to obtain a deeper knowledge of the market and enhance the credibility of the brand. In addition, having a robust online presence and using digital marketing methods may be an effective means of reaching these consumers. 